title: RealWifeStories - Valentina Nappi (This Partys Boring) NEW 29 Ma
description:
Valentina loves to have a good time. Too bad she's married to a guy who drags her to boring parties with boring people. Sick of stale conversation and charades, she seduces the host's husband while everybody else is downstairs. It's not long until another guest's husband comes looking for them and decides to join their private party.
